Title: Visconti 18410 Large Tan Leather Messenger Bag Shoulder Bag Organizer Briefcase
Description: Visconti 18410 Large Tan Leather Messenger Bag Shoulder Bag Organizer Briefcase Brand: Visconti Collection: Hunter Style Number: 18410Tan Color: Oil Tan MSRP: $176.99 ·A Hunter Messenger Bag in Oiled leather from the popular Visconti brand·COLOR Distressed looking mud brown/oil tan Size 10.2" length 11.8" Height 3.2 Depth"·Full length front flap with a center magnetic snap to hold it shut·2 closed pockets + zipped pocked and open folder for papers under flap, rear zipped pocket as well as nice size internal pocket with divider·Smooth oiled leather with Double and Contrast stitching The 18410 is a stylish Messenger bag from the U.K. "Visconti" brand. The bag is made from top quality leather and contrast stitching. It comes with an adjustable long 50" shoulder strap to comfortably fit the tall and the short and there is a sliding rubber shoulder grip for comfort when carrying heavy loads. The 18410 has a full front flap held down securely with a magnetic center brass snap. Under the flap and as well at the rear of the bag there is a wide zipped pocket across the width of the bag .There is also an open folder for slipping in a newspaper, paper notebook or manila envelopes. As well there are 2 convenient pockets for a cell phone and a music player just under the flap of the bag. The main compartment of the bag has 2 sections which can comfortably accommodate an ipad with2/3 books/textbooks . There is yet another zipped pocket for important documents on the opposite side of the bag. All in all it makes for the perfect organizer bag. The color of the leather is a stylish distressed looking mud brown, it also has a stylish professional look to it that can be used for office / business or school. The bag may have wrinkles, scars, scratches that are inherent characteristics and natural beauty of the hide enhancing its special distressed look.
